Package: halfedgedatastructr
Title: Provide a half-edge data structure for a 3d convex polytope
Version: 0.0.0.9003
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeff", "Lansing", , "lansing2357@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A convex hull data structure is converted into a half-edge data
  structure (he_ds). The he_ds provides operations cut and fold, which apply either
  an outer (cut) or an inner (fold) spanning tree to the he_ds. See the vignettes
  for details.
